oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mr. DeeJay U.S.A. - 1953-12-04 - Part 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WSM program Mr. DeeJay U.S.A., originally broadcast December 4, 1953, part 2. This episode spotlights Justin Tubb's 'Country Music Clubhouse' show, usually broadcast over WHIN, Gallatin, TN. Featuring announcer Grant Turner with guest Ray Price.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Hank Locklin; Faron Young; Ray Price
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Let Me Be The One (Hank Locklin) (recording) -- Justin Tubb, Bill Carrigan, and Grant Turner talk -- You're The Angel On My Christmas Tree (Faron Young) (recording) -- Justin Tubb and Ray Price talk -- You Always Get By (Ray Price) (recording) -- Closing statement (Justin Tubb, Grant Turner)
